| Capability | File | What It Does |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| LLM wrapper | [llm.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/_core/llm.ts) | `invokeLLM` — supports `image_url`, `file_url` (PDF, audio, video) natively |
| Floor plan analysis | [floor-plan-analyzer.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/design/floor-plan-analyzer.ts) | Gemini Vision → room breakdown, areas, spatial ratios |
| PDF extraction | [pdf-extraction.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/pdf-extraction.ts) | Gemini Vision → room extraction from floor plans |
| Design advisor | [ai-design-advisor.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/design/ai-design-advisor.ts) | Gemini → per-space material recommendations |
| Visual generation | [visual-gen.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/visual-gen.ts) | Project data → mood board and render prompts |
| Structured JSON output | [llm.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/_core/llm.ts) | `outputSchema` forces Gemini to return typed JSON |

### What's Missing (Must Be Built)

| Gap | Why It's Needed |
|-----|----------------|
| **File upload infrastructure** | No server-side S3 SDK. Need upload → signed URL → store pipeline |
| **AI Intake Engine** | New engine that processes multimodal assets → [ProjectInputs](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/shared/miyar-types.ts#36-102) |
| **Project assets table** | Permanent storage of uploaded files (images, PDFs, voice) on the project |
| **Intake router** | New tRPC router exposing the AI intake workflow |
| **Intake UI** | Canvas-style upload zone + chat interface on the New Project page |

