#### 5. Frontend: Redesigned New Project Experience

##### Option A — "Talk to MIYAR" (default for new users)

**File:** `client/src/pages/NewProject.tsx` — full rewrite

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  MIYAR 2.0 — New Project                        │
│                                                  │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│  │  Drop files here or paste URLs              │ │
│  │  📎 Images · 📄 PDFs · 🎤 Voice · 🔗 URLs  │ │
│  │                                              │ │
│  │  [Upload Files]  [Paste URL]  [Record Voice] │ │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│                                                  │
│  💬 Or tell us about your project:              │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│  │  "50 luxury apartments in Dubai Marina,      │ │
│  │   Japandi style, targeting HNWI buyers..."   │ │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│                                                  │
│  [Analyze & Auto-Fill ✨]                       │
│                                                  │
│  ─── OR ───                                     │
│  [Skip to Manual Form →]                        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

After AI processes, transitions to the existing 7-step form, but **pre-filled** with:
- Green badges on AI-populated fields (high confidence)
- Yellow badges on fields needing review
- "Why this value?" tooltips showing AI reasoning
- Uploaded assets visible as thumbnails in a sidebar panel

##### Option B — Expert Mode (unchanged)

Same 7-step wizard as today. But each section gets a small "AI Assist" button that can:
- Auto-fill just that section from uploaded assets or typed description
- Suggest a value based on the data already entered

##### Option C — Quick Brief

Text area or voice recorder → AI fills 60-70% → developer completes remaining fields manually.

