## Build Sequence

| Phase | What | Key Files | Dependencies |
|-------|------|-----------|-------------|
| **2.0-A** | Schema + File Upload Infrastructure | [drizzle/schema.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/drizzle/schema.ts), `server/routers/intake.ts` (getUploadUrl) | S3 credentials in [.env](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/.env) |
| **2.0-B** | AI Intake Engine | `server/engines/intake/ai-intake-engine.ts`, `url-scraper.ts` | Existing `invokeLLM`, [floor-plan-analyzer.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/design/floor-plan-analyzer.ts) |
| **2.0-C** | Intake Router (full) | `server/routers/intake.ts` (processAssets, refineWithChat) | 2.0-A + 2.0-B |
| **2.0-D** | Frontend — Upload + AI canvas | `client/src/pages/NewProject.tsx` rewrite | 2.0-C, existing [ProjectForm.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/components/ProjectForm.tsx) unchanged |
| **2.0-E** | AI Assist buttons on existing form | [client/src/components/ProjectForm.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/components/ProjectForm.tsx) enhancements | 2.0-B |
| **2.0-F** | Asset gallery on project detail | [client/src/pages/ProjectDetail.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/pages/ProjectDetail.tsx) | 2.0-A |

> [!WARNING]
> **Phase 10 (Sales Premium)** should be built **before** MIYAR 2.0. The 2.0 intake system is a product philosophy shift — it benefits from having all downstream engines fully operational first. Phase 10 adds ~4 files; MIYAR 2.0 touches ~15+ files.

