## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **S3 setup**: MIYAR currently has no server-side S3 SDK. We need AWS S3 credentials for file storage. Alternatively, we could use Vercel Blob Storage which requires zero AWS config. Which do you prefer?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Phase sequencing**: I recommend building Phase 10 first (4 files, ~2 sessions), then starting MIYAR 2.0. Reason: the Sales Premium engine adds value to the Investor Summary immediately, and MIYAR 2.0 benefits from having all downstream engines complete. Do you agree?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Voice input**: Browser native `MediaRecorder` API can capture audio → send to Gemini as `file_url` with `audio/mp4` mime type. Gemini transcribes and interprets natively. No third-party speech-to-text needed. Is voice input a P0 or can it come later?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Scope check**: Should the chat refinement feature (Path 3 — "refineWithChat") be in the initial release, or can it come as a fast follow? It's the most complex piece and could delay the core upload → auto-fill flow.
